Security:
- Add JWT auth to /api/chat (Edge-compatible, reduced rate for unauthenticated)
- Add auth gate to /api/document-upload, use auth email instead of client-supplied
- Fix sanitize() to use HTML entity encoding instead of tag stripping
- Add timing-safe comparison to auth/index.js SuiteDash/Neon code checks
- Add requireJson/rejectOversizedBody to auth/reset-code.js
- Require organization_id on admin API key listing
- Add Stripe webhook idempotency (dedup by event.id)
- Return 500 on Stripe webhook processing failure (was always 200)
- Redact secrets (accessCode, hostingPassword) from provision.js response
- Fix rate limiter eviction (evict oldest 50% instead of full clear)
- Remove SMS-to-email bug in document-upload.js

Backend:
- resolveEntityType returns null for unknown types (was defaulting to LLC)
- Fix computeObligations null dereference on failed obligation creation
- Fix evaluateObligation returning stale status after transitions
- Fix provision.js metadata clobber (merge existing before update)
- Replace bare fetch with fetchWithTimeout in provision.js (8s timeout)
- Add 5s timeouts to all health check external calls
- Use N8N_HEALTH from _config.js in health.js
- Fix nonprofit fee display in notification templates

Frontend:
- Add Entities tab to portal mobile bottom nav
- Fix fake compliance score (show N/A on API failure instead of 88)
- Add session expired toast before silent logout
- Fix settings claim: 'stored locally' instead of 'saved automatically'
- Fix admin login bypass on network error (stay on login screen)
- Add res.ok checks to admin callAPI/adminFetch
- Add admin logout button and session management
- Add hamburger aria-expanded to admin.html, 404.html, about.html
- Fix newsletter error CSS selector (sibling, not child)
- Add responsive breakpoint for pricing grid (mobile overflow)
- Add prefers-reduced-motion to site.css
